### AI Story Generator - API Tests
### Use the REST Client VS Code extension to run these

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### Root
GET {{baseUrl}}/

###

### Generate Story - Robot in forest
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/story/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "A lonely robot discovers a hidden forest."
}

###

### Generate Story - Dragon and child
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/story/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "A dragon becomes best friends with a village child."
}

###

### Generate Story - Astronaut on Mars
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/story/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "A lonely astronaut finds a message in a bottle on Mars."
}

###

### Test validation - prompt too short (should return 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/story/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Hi"
}
